

      <div class="rules text-center pt-3" style="font-family: Permanent Marker; margin:auto" >
          <h2 style="font-family: Permanent Marker" >LES REGLES DU FIGHT CLUB</h2>
          <ul style="list-style: none">
            <li>The first rule of Fight Club is: You do not talk about Fight Club.</li>
            <li>The second rule of Fight Club is: You do not talk about Fight Club.</li>
            <li>Third rule of Fight Club: someone yells stop, goes limp, taps out, the fight is over.</li>
            <li>Fourth rule: only two guys to a fight.</li>
            <li>Fifth rule: one fight at a time, fellas.</li>
            <li>Sixth rule: no shirts, no shoes.</li>
            <li>Seventh rule: fights will go on as long as they have to.</li>
            <li>And the eighth and final rule: if this is your first night at Fight Club, <strong>you have to fight</strong>.</li>
          </ul>
      </div>

    <div class= "content">
      <div class="cards">
        <% @arenass.each do |arena| %>
            <% if !arena.photo.nil? %>
              <div class="card-category" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.2)),
           url('<%= cl_image_path arena.photo, height: 300, width: 400, crop: :fill %>')">
                <h2><%= link_to arena.title, arena_path(arena) %></h2>
              </div>
            <% else %>
              <div class="card-category" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.2)),
           url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519741347686-c1e0aadf4611?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1980&q=80')">
                <h2><%= link_to arena.title, arena_path(arena) %></h2>
              </div>
            <% end %>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      <div
        id="map"
        style="width: 100%;
        height: 600px;"
        data-markers="<%= @markers.to_json %>"
        data-mapbox-api-key="<%= ENV['MAPBOX_API_KEY'] %>">
      </div>
    </div>

